The Zondo Commission will continue to hear Denel related testimony from the Former Denel Group Chief Executive Officer and current GCEO Tlib Sadik, Stephan Burger, and also from, Daniel Mantsha.  JOHANNESBURG - The state capture commission will continue to hear Denel-related testimony on Thursday. WATCH: State capture inquiry to hear Denel-related testimony The commission is expected to hear testimony from current interim Denel Group CEO Talib Sadik, former Chief Executive Officer of Denel Land Systems Stephan Burger and former board chairperson Daniel Mantsha.